Package: dataViewer
Type: Package
Title: RStudio Addin for viewing data and identifying outliers
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Who wrote it
Maintainer: Daniel Padfield <dp323@exeter.ac.uk>
Description: dataViewer is an RStudio Addin that allows you to interactively explore your dataframe within R and identify points of interest that need further examination through clicking. It was designed to work specificially with non-linear models where evaluating fits is difficult and viewing the data to identify potential outliers is critical.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.1)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Imports: miniUI,
    shiny,
    ggplot2,
    tidyr
